{"tid":28877,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向西村上春樹：所有國企以後不會「裁員」","createTime":"2016-12-08T08:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T08:53:00.000Z","uid":30807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dab3f14943d141a8e3bdb88c8746165e3b97cf0d","tid":28877,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:15:36.000Z","msg":"「優化」一詞在大陸早已被濫用，無論「改進」、「改良」、「改善」、「美化」還是「強化」，大陸喜歡只以「優化」一詞取而代之。現在，大陸連裁員都成為「優化」的一種，多間國企無論炒幾多人，都拒絕承認裁員，辯稱是「人員優化」或「內部優化」。<br />\n<br />\n樂視體育被傳裁員20%，公司只承認是進行「人員優化」。携程網早前被指裁員數百人，官方回應指沒有裁員，只是僅「優化」146人。搜狐、暴風科技及國美都先後把大批員工辭退，但沒有一間說自己是裁員，而是正常的「人手優化」。<br />\n<br />\n有冠冕堂皇的措辭「優化」一下，事實就仿佛不存在。大陸其實沒有強姦，強姦只是與陌生人「主動生育」，就算殺人放火，也不過是「協助過身」。大陸要和平，真的很容易，香港要跟上這種和諧的步伐，亦早已不難矣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/xxharuki/photos/a.353973134660312.82213.142564715801156/1243653892358894/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fxxharuki%2Fphotos%2Fa.353973134660312.82213.142564715801156%2F1243653892358894%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=XBtCiekKnBD61yqLsWuThKEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=5f8b50f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/xxharuki/photos/a.353973134660312.82213.142564715801156/1243653892358894/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"6a184a22dfa214f467775b465fe81b41020d64ab","tid":28877,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一鍵留名"},{"pid":"feffc1e2d24aade9c82697ad0fb0caacaa23f55e","tid":28877,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f2448c91cfd3c883affc2156b031b61bb78957","tid":28877,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:24:47.000Z","msg":"蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"